So when collecting your historical blue and
deciding what you want to collect whether

00:00:02.810 --> 00:00:07.910
it's going to be on teapots whether it's going
to be teapots and sugar bowls and creamers

00:00:07.910 --> 00:00:12.530
or if your going to have a wide range of tableware.
